vooga.towerdefense.action

Class Action

  • java.lang.Object
    • vooga.towerdefense.action.Action
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExampleAttackAction, FindTargets, FollowPath, LaunchProjectile, MakeElement, ModifyAttributeValue, Move, MoveToDestination, OnAttributeValue, OnDeath, PaintAttributes, PeriodicAction, RandomChance, RemoveGameElement, SetAttributeValue, SpawnEnemy, TargetedModifyAttributeAction

    public abstract class Action
extends Object
    An AbstractAction is superclassed to define specific Actions that can be taken by game elements. This includes attacks, upgrades, path creation and anything the developer may wish to implement.
    Author:
    Matthew Roy, XuRui, Zhen Gou
